  "keyFeatures": [
    "Spring-based physics animations with natural motion",
    "Re-targetable animations that preserve velocity during interruptions",
    "Block-based API similar to UIView.animate",
    "Property-based animator API for custom animations",
    "Support for UIKit, SwiftUI, and AppKit",
    "Gesture velocity integration for smooth interactions",
    "ProMotion 120fps animation support",
    "Zero external dependencies"
